      <div class="wrap reveal"><div class="c"><p class="eyebrow">Tracing Roots</p><h2>More than a trip.</h2><p>From Soweto and the Apartheid Museum to the Cape's layered history, the journey follows the through-line that defines Diaspora Echo — African resistance, memory, and triumph. The luxury is the headline; the roots are the reason.</p><div class="chips" style="margin-top:16px"><span>Soweto</span><span>Vilakazi Street</span><span>Apartheid Museum</span><span>Constitution Hill</span><span>District Six</span></div></div></div></section>
